{"tid":590900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9錢正經mode] 扮民必須得到本土自決港獨endorse才能前進！！","createTime":"2018-03-13T05:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T23:21:50.000Z","uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2d4f3069958b6061c7866359ed3b29e1a14092","tid":590900,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我9錢SARS自由痕之後已經提出香港開始政治代溝明顯化，尤其ProDemo！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一班該上IFC排隊既民主回西老撚心知肚明，害左年青少以後各代，稍仲有良知如李怡老練會早認錯兼出來幫拖，但大部分始終支那優秀DNA，一邊死撐一邊用腳投票，更甚者索性做真正中蟈人－投共瀨共自J&quot;為俊傑&quot;！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過去廿年無數次研究探索以至簡單目測，基本上70後80後打後都係愈支持本土自決之類，從剩餘時間角度睇，呢班人既未來遠大重要間個一大班埋岸但行將就木既老撚老固執老支那！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSo，試問各界扮民大台，冇呢班愈黎愈多兼愈黎愈興既本土甚至焦土endorse你，你地點行落去？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（當然，存心做狗戲子厄飯食草錢買豪宅等走人，或旨在攪生意如李華明賣佢個2粒丸除外！！！)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d53ec2e8f0d223fe49f6146226de0d2e43256314","tid":590900,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎討論！！岩聽推下！！！Thx！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b557a3fa3692e51523e31ad00d80326e0ae65eb9","tid":590900,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎討論！！岩聽推下！！！Thx！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff52e0efc526dbaf711b785b3a49a320ddf0fd87","tid":590900,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎討論！！岩聽推下！！！Thx！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class